积极性。 您在建议中提出「建议国家率先在东北地区全面放开人口生育限制」对我委工作很有参考价值。我委认为，东北地区可以立足本地实际进行探索，组织专家进行研究，深入研判全面放开生育限制对当地经济增长、社会和谐稳定、资源环境战略、基本公共服务等方面的影响；做好政策调整后人口变动测算；研究实施全面放开生育政策需要配套出台的文件；评估政策变动的社会风险等等。在此基础上，提出东北地区实施全面生育政策的试点方案。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-d202d1ff9e45c3161a26d78a22f5391c_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1305 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/445095765"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIyLnQ/YO8pr5rEAMaCDYxMTg4ODc3ILjauYEGMKcBOMgqQAJyCTQ0NTA5NTc2NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1613736403.1632779", "card_id": "Q_445222303", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 110}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "中方公布涉加勒万河谷冲突消息出于怎样考量？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "在 19 日举行的外交部例行记者会上，有记者就此事提问称，今天解放军报刊发了一篇综合性的报道，证实中印在去年 6 月的边境冲突当中，中方有 4 名官兵牺牲，1 名团长受重伤，请问中方在此时公布相关消息的考量是怎样的？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-62849daba0bd884d46090e4bd6a4f39f_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1282 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/445222303"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyLnQ/YO8pr5rEAMaCDYxMjE3MTQxII7pvYEGMAs4rgRAA3IJNDQ1MjIyMzAzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1613736403.163699", "card_id": "Q_444675805", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 1233}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "年轻人不结婚到底侵犯了谁的利益？为啥全社会都在逼婚？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-efe5eca52e6ec7b0d89f662b5e550de4_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1239 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/444675805"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyLnQ/YO8pr5rEAMaCDYxMDk1NDg1IKPUrIEGMG44pyRABHIJNDQ0Njc1ODA1eACq